.IP \(bu 2
How to update all outdated packages?
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
$ macdaily update \-\-all
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
.UNINDENT
