.IP \(bu 2
How to uninstall a certain package along with its dependencies (eg:
\fIpytest\fP from brewed CPython version 3.6)?
.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.nf
.ft C
$ macdaily uninstall pip \e
      \-\-brew \-\-cpython \-\-python=3\&.6 \-\-packages=pytest
.ft P
.fi
.UNINDENT
